thread.title: Kimberly
thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Kimberly

author: Kimberly
title: Kimberly
text: Manager was very nice and helpful. Worked with our situation and made everything as easy as possible. The unit was clean and secure and very easy to get to. There are lights all over the place so it was easy moving things when the sun had gone down. Only thing was that there weren't mirrors to see around corners when driving but that's just being picky. Great experience and will use place again when needed.
